{"tid":1761951,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"潘杰寧呢隻老雞見到凱晴上位係咪好酸溜溜呢？","createTime":"2019-11-29T08:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T09:38:48.000Z","uid":96525,"like":81,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e302297783d0b7b34664864f49bebd0a49d5be8b","tid":1761951,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"人地靚又靚過你，後生又後生過你，波又大過你，你只係一件又醜樣腳又粗呃毒撚嘅老雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你平時咁憎曼聯，而家見到個後生女獌迷上位一定好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫班毒撚呵返你啦臭老雞掃把星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS:之前世界盃睇電視見到你條老雞真係好唔開胃，希望你有自知之明咪撚再做幕前，thx杰寧公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441f6f48af6e764b2606130692e14f309d6a3ace","tid":1761951,"uid":283207,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:49:24.000Z","msg":"佢塊西反哂皮....好醜怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79b6792f6faf9b616b56aa5db19915aa39bee19","tid":1761951,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:49:36.000Z","msg":"佢都比牙佳殺左仲點酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649f2b88071b9d3ccaba4032a5fb9ffad555ab8b","tid":1761951,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"441f6f48af6e764b2606130692e14f309d6a3ace","tid":1761951,"uid":283207,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:49:24.000Z","msg"